name: Spirit of Dark Magic
effect:
While this card is on the field, its Level becomes 7.
When your opponent activates a card or effect, while you control "Dark Magician" (Quick Effect): You can send this card from your hand or field to the GY; negate the activation, and if you do, destroy that card.
If this card is in your GY, and you control "Dark Magician": You can Special Summon this card.
You can only use each effect of "Spirit of Dark Magic" once per turn.
